content.rendered:
Directed by Vipin Das

Written by Vipin Das. Nashid Mohamed Famy. Ajith Kumar

Cast Basil Joseph (Rajesh).Anand Manmadhan.Noby Marcose.Azees Nedumangad.Sudheer Paravoor.Harish Pengan.Manju Pillai. Darshana Rajendran (Jaya).Sarath Sabha.Aju Varghese

Languages Malayalam

Producers Ganesh Menon. Amal Paulson. Lakshmi Warrier

Production Cheers Entertainments. Sooper Dooper Films
